{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5180", "repo": "rails", "body": "I recently had this issue too, not many people seem to experience this behavior\r\n\r\nTry adding a blank line in your application.css before all the requires\r\ni.e.\r\n/*\r\n * This is a manifest file that'll automatically include all the stylesheets available in this directory\r\n * and any sub-directories. You're free to add application-wide styles to this file and they'll appear at\r\n * the top of the compiled file, but it's generally better to create a new file per style scope.\r\n *\r\n *= require fonts\r\n *= require core\r\n * ...\r\n*/\r\n\r\nThat worked for me, wtf?", "_id": {"$oid": "52381bbdbd3543c15100e436"}, "issue_id": 5180, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5099552", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5180#issuecomment-5099552", "updated_at": "2012-04-12T20:08:41Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa", "login": "jassa", "gravatar_id": "17ed6dc692c92af19e8b9dbf39163bb7", "html_url": "https://github.com/jassa", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/17ed6dc692c92af19e8b9dbf39163bb7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F88405b5d2cfec4d18575beda9f294a8d.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 368802, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jassa/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-04-12T20:08:41Z", "id": 5099552, "owner": "rails"}
